123
00:08:10,420 --> 00:08:11,520
I want to return to Jasmine Villa.

124
00:08:12,590 --> 00:08:14,560
I still want to experience being an Empress.

125
00:08:55,250 --> 00:08:56,570
♪Drifting back through the snow♪

126
00:08:56,570 --> 00:08:59,690
♪Dreams end, seeking the unseen mountain♪

127
00:09:02,530 --> 00:09:03,650
♪Slowly walking away♪

128
00:09:03,850 --> 00:09:08,010
♪Dust and frost cover your eyes♪

129
